node.text:
If you know me you know I’m never one to do things by halves and my baby shower was no exception, 8 months pregnant or not!!
Thank you so much to everyone who made it possible, who brought my ideas to life (@createdbysp_ ) & ensured my day was completely stress free (bar swollen feet lol) 
Thank you to our family & friends, I appreciate every single one of you 💗
Thank you to @addai_eye_ for this video & everyone else listed in the credits, every single one of you are the reason it was so special!!!
